	<div class="commentbody">
      <p>What is the typical relative signal power of wifi routers vs wifi client devices? While I&#8217;m not usually near my router, I do tend to leave my keys and wallet on my desk within a few inches of my laptop when I&#8217;m at work. Similarly, they are often near my phone (a wifi client) on my person when I&#8217;m not at work. I&#8217;m assuming the power output of those devices are less than the router, though, so I still don&#8217;t know if that would be enough. If it was though, then I might still find these useful, I just wish the team were upfront about these sorts of limitations.</p>

